            OnPremiseProperty = new AzureNextGen.AzureData.V20190724Preview.Inputs.OnPremisePropertyArgs

                PublicSigningKey = "publicOnPremSigningKey",
            },
            ResourceGroupName = "testrg",
            Tags =

            },
        });
    }

}
